{"ticker": "REVOLUT_GROUP_HOLDINGS_LTD", "company": "Revolut Group Holdings LTD", "weight_sum": 1.23, "etfs": ["ARKVX", "ARKSX", "ARKUX"], "is_private": true, "query": "\"Revolut\" -is:retweet min_faves:10 since_time:1777776343 until_time:1777789565", "n_fetched": 1, "n_kept": 1, "n_dropped": 0, "kept": [{"type": "tweet", "id": "2050805671570841913", "url": "https://x.com/revolut20/status/2050805671570841913", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/revolut20/status/2050805671570841913", "text": "For years, crypto has positioned itself as the future of finance but everyday usability has remained a challenge. Bridging that gap is what will ultimately drive true adoption.\n\n\ud83d\udd25This is where @KoloHub stands out.\n\n\ud83d\udc49By enabling users to spend digital assets such as BTC, ETH, and USDC seamlessly through a Visa/Mastercard-powered card, Kolo transforms crypto from a passive holding into an active financial tool. Payments are processed with automatic fiat conversion at the point of sale, making the experience as intuitive as any traditional card transaction.\n\n\ud83d\udd25The integration with Apple Pay and Google Pay further simplifies usage, allowing for quick, contactless payments across millions of merchants globally. Combined with availability in over 150 countries, the accessibility is notable.\n\n\ud83d\udd25Additional features such as up to 5% Bitcoin cashback, transparent pricing with no hidden fees, and support for both custodial and non custodial wallets reflect a well rounded approach to user needs.\n\n\ud83d\udc49What is particularly compelling is the roadmap. The introduction of personal IBANs, SWIFT capabilities, and expanded mobile applications suggests a transition toward a more comprehensive financial ecosystem with not just a payment solution, but a broader infrastructure for managing digital and traditional assets.\n\nAs the industry evolves, solutions that prioritize simplicity, accessibility, and real world functionality will define th